com.sidemash.redson

Interface JsonValue

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    JsonLiteral, JsonStructure
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsonArray, JsonBoolean, JsonNull, JsonNumber, JsonObject, JsonOptional, JsonString

    public interface JsonValue
    The root interface in the Redson json hierarchy. JsonValue is a supertype of all json types.
